Knight Moves;;1992;;R;;Crime,Drama,Mystery;;6.1;;Carl Schenkel;;Christopher Lambert,Tom Skerritt,Codie Lucas Wilbee,Joshua Murray,Frank C. Turner,Don Thompson,Megan Leitch,Alex Diakun,Ferdy Mayne,Katharine Isabelle,Mark Wilson,Kehli O'Byrne,Daniel Baldwin,Blu Mankuma,Monica Marko,Walter Marsh,Charles Bailey-Gates,Arthur Brauss;;A chess grandmaster is in a big tournament, and when his lover is found painted up and the blood drained out of her body he becomes a chief suspect. After he gets a call from the killer urging him to try and figure out the game, he cooperates with police and a psychologist to try and catch the killer, but doubts linger about the grandmaster's innocence as the string of grisly murders continues.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0104627/